sentences: Chris Knutson is an American stand-up comedian from Minneapolis, Minnesota.
Patrick Strait of City Pages said that "Knutson has established himself as one of the most consistently funny performers" in the Midwest.
Knutson began performing improv comedy in 2006, and stand-up in 2009.
He won Acme Comedy Company's "Funniest Person in the Twin Cities" contest in 2010.
